&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/dntco43u/med_exam"&gt;https://github.com/dntco43u/med_exam&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:1" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink"&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>grafana</title><link>https://hu.gvp6nx1a.duckdns.org/infra/grafana/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hu.gvp6nx1a.duckdns.org/infra/grafana/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="데모-페이지"&gt;데모 페이지&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%eb%8d%b0%eb%aa%a8-%ed%8e%98%ec%9d%b4%ec%a7%80" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
